4.12 Important Notes
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. Users are LOCAL (not LDAP) - Table 3 specifies local users
2. /public: guests can read (guest ok = yes), authenticated can write
3. /internal: only jamie (valid users = jamie)
4. Permissions:
- public: 1777 (sticky bit prevents deletion by others)
- internal: 770 (only jamie and group)
5. Samba passwords stored in tdbsam (not system passwords)
6. For testing from jamie-ws01, routing must work (check Step 2)
7. DNS must resolve int-srv01.int.ws.kz (check Step 3)
